        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9">
                Mr. Eric Fletcher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister to what extent the terms of reference of the Royal Commission on Taxation of Profits and Income were changed on the initiative of Lord Waverley; and whether, in view of Lord Waverley's resignation from the Commission, he will now restore the original terms of reference.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-3384d166-65f6-4bbb-a706-6acc9dfd72b9">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>







<div class="content-item other-content">
        <!-- START statement -->
        <div class="statement col-md-9  content-container " id='contribution-53c514c2-b4e8-48ff-9859-cafc375b5afa'>
            
<p class="">46 and 47.</p>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            </div>
        <div class="clearfix"></div>
        <!-- END statement -->
</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
                Mr. Douglas Jay
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">asked the Prime Minister (1) how far it was at the request of Lord Waverley that the terms of reference of the Royal Commission on Taxation of Profits and Income were altered;<p></p> (2) whether he will now restore the original terms of reference of the Royal Commission on Taxation of Profits and Income.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-357ea044-6fe4-435e-8011-e2301e802a27">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
                The Prime Minister (Mr. Winston Churchill)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">I see no occasion to make any further change in the terms of reference. The amendment was made in agreement with Lord Waverley, but the same point had been raised by the former Chairman, Lord Cohen, in a letter to the right hon. Gentleman the Member for Leeds, South (Mr. Gaitskell), then Chancellor of the Exchequer, on 20th April. He did not <span id="649" class="column-number" data-column-number="649"></span> dissent from the interpretation placed upon the terms of reference by Lord Cohen. This has now been made explicit.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-cfb19cd8-4b35-4a11-81b8-8464a9c7ee40">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
</div>





<div class="content-item" id="contribution-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-9 multiple-edit-warning">
        <div class="alert alert-warning" id="warning-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>This content has already been edited and is awaiting review.
        </div>
    </div>

        <div class="col-md-9 nohighlight member-container">
            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
                Mr. Fletcher
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Is not the change in the terms of reference a sinister and unnecessary attempt to invite the Commission to make recommendations in accordance with Lord Waverley's well-known political views on the amount of revenue raised from taxation; and ought not the Prime Minister now to restore the original terms of reference?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1952-03-06/debates/094551fc-bcb6-46eb-a41e-6a42ed07b541/RoyalCommissionOnTaxation(TermsOfReference)#contribution-33a36313-472c-44d4-b349-749076e0f159">
                            <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div>&nbsp;Share
                        </a>
                    </div>

        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
